channel.desc: The NASCAR Xfinity Series returns to Texas Motor Speedway for the Andy's Frozen Custard 300. Connor Zilisch's spinout caused the Ag-Pro 300 at Talledega to require to a photo finish, with Austin Hill edging out Jesse Love and Jeb Burton for the win.
